mcrcon.c:576:2: warning: ‘strncpy’ specified bound 4096 equals destination size [-Wstringop-truncation]
  strncpy(packet.data, s1, DATA_BUFFSIZE);
  ^~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
```
